Package org.radixware.jiraclient.wrap

Main interfaces of JIRA client and JIRA objects (immutable).

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Action
    Representation of JIRA workflow action (for ex.: default actions "Start Progress", "Close Issue", "Resolve Issue" and etc).
    Attachment
    Representation of JIRA attachment.
    Comment
    JIRA issue comment.
    CustomField
    Interface represents custom fields in JIRA.
    Issue
    Representation of JIRA issue.
    IssueType
    Representation of JIRA issue type (for ex.: bug, task, question, improvement and etc).
    JiraClient
    Remote client of JIRA.
    ParentIssue
    Parent issue containing references to all subtasks.
    Priority
    Representation of issue priority (for ex.: blocker, minor, info request and etc.).
    Project
    Information about JIRA project.
    Resolution
    Representation of issue resolution (state of workflow).
    SearchFilter
    Searching filter.
    Status
    Representation of issues status (state of workflow).
    Subtask
    Subtask.
    User
    Information about specified JIRA user.
    Version
    Version of JIRA project.
    Worklog
    Information about the work done.
